data.title: Mollösund - round trip
data.meta_description: Go on an exciting sightseeing tour and discover wonderful Mollösund! Book an excursion with Askard Hav & Land now!
data.text:
Take in the breathtaking beauty of the archipelago at Askard Hav & land's round trip to the fishing camp in Mollösund. The tour departs from Stenungsund, Askerö islands or Almösund and takes you on a journey through the Stigfjorden, which is one of the region's most fantastic landscapes with wonderful nature.

During the three-hour tour, you will gain fascinating insights into the area's history, culture and traditions. And once in Mollösund, the captain tells us more about the fishing camp and its importance.

If you have clothes that are adapted to the weather, you can stay comfortable throughout the activity. During your time on the boat, you may spot marine wildlife depending on the season, so bring your camera to capture some great photos!
